name: Faeline Stomp
description:
Strike the ground fiercely to expose a faeline for 30 sec, dealing 213 Nature damage to up to 5 enemies, and restores 5,127 health to up to 5 allies within 30 yds caught in the faeline. Stagger is 5% more effective for 8 sec against enemies caught in the faeline suffer an additional 345 damage.

Your abilities have a 6% chance of resetting the cooldown of Faeline Stomp while fighting on a faeline.
